OOC: before I start, i want everybody to know, last night my gf bought me the 
scourge/x-brawn 2-pack! scourge immediately became spychanger laser op ( 
painting was a breeze) and brawn kicked major ass! (show accurate) ^_^ 

       Ghost lands in bonebreaker, and proceeds to disengage. the links 
buckle, and a jolt of electricity blasts out, striking the exposed metal of 
one of panthero's cat's unfineshed god armors.
Goth: ghost! cut it out! what the hell are you doing?!? ( leaps behind the 
finished armor.)
ghost: i'm not doing this! this armor has lost it! i'm locked in! it's 
draining something out...of.....(loses conciousness)
goth: GHOST! WAKE UP! ( jumps onto the armor, trying to wrestle it to the 
ground)
the armor easily fights goth off, causing him great damage in the process. it 
then stands straight up and ejects ghost's near sparkless, unconcious body. 
the armor twitches, then shivers, then begins to convulse uncontrollably. 
when this subsides, he transforms to elephant mode and begins leaving max 
city.
OOC: now it's your turn! ^_^ (you know who i'm talking about!) also, i'd 
reccomend the two members of P.C. that ordered godarmors come get them.




--part1_12b.bfacda0.299537b4_boundary
